sentences.english: Tonight, stay in 3-star Xiyu Yongsheng Hotel or equivalent.
sentences.chinese: 今晚，住宿于桃园山庄或同级3星酒店。

sentences.english: The possibilities of product allocation in the same-level supply network were discussed.
sentences.chinese: 论述了同级供应网络中产品调剂的可能性。

sentences.english: Creative unique tool pot supporting and also process the minimum driving power of same level tool magazine.
sentences.chinese: 创新独特刀套支撑方式，拥有小于同级刀库的驱动力。

sentences.english: Four additional ships of the same class have been approved.
sentences.chinese: 另外还有四艘同级舰艇也已批准建造。

sentences.english: Look at the pictures in Section A and Section B. Review the following sentences.
sentences.chinese: 利用图片或实物复习同级比较的用法。

sentences.english: The only checking we can do of UML-like diagrams is peer review.
sentences.chinese: 而我们对UML之类的图表唯一能做的就是同级检查。

sentences.english: Party committees are responsible, and report their work, to the Party congresses at their respective levels.
sentences.chinese: 党的各级委员会向同级的代表大会负责并报告工作。

sentences.english: Equivalent level trade union representatives shall participate in district labour dispute arbitration organizations.
sentences.chinese: 地方劳动争议仲裁组织应当有同级工会代表参加。

sentences.english: Only peer-reviewed literature in English language was in¬cluded.
sentences.chinese: 纳入的都是同级别的英文回顾性文献。

sentences.english: Use bulleted or numbered lists for items in a series.
sentences.chinese: 把同级的观点以项目符号或编号的形式排列。

sentences.english: Local Party congresses are convened by the Party committees at the corresponding levels.
sentences.chinese: 党的地方各级代表大会由同级党的委员会召集。

sentences.english: It's also pretty musical by the standards of its peers.
sentences.chinese: 以它的同级功放标准衡量，它同样有着相当的音乐性。

definition: to skip a grade/to bypass ranks/to go over the head of one's boss
